message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper focuses on using deep learning techniques for medical image segmentation, specifically for pancreatic cyst segmentation in abdominal CT scans. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of deep supervision and gradient back-propagation also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), or cs.NEURON (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the medical application of the paper suggests that it could also belong to cs.MED (Medical Imaging).
